    {
      "id": "ci_68967917e6d8819590c9d9da8bc2c97c0c76117201fbe909",
      "code": "original_full = \"وَإِذْ أَخَذَ رَبُّكَ مِنْ بَنِي آدَمَ مِنْهُمْ إِنَّهُمْ كَفَرُوا وَأَخْبَرَهُمْ بِالْعَذَابِ الْأَخِيرِ وَأَعْتَذَرُوا فَأَخَذَتْهُمْ الْغَمَّةُ فَأَخَذَ رَبُّكَ مِنْهُمْ أَشْرَعَهُمْ فَأَصْبَحُوا أَهْلَ الْفَلَكِ الْمُسْتَقِيمِ\"\n\ncandidate = search_quran_by_substring(query1)[0]['ayah_text']\n\ndef token_f1(a, b):\n    na = normalize_ar(a).split()\n    nb = normalize_ar(b).split()\n    from collections import Counter\n    ca, cb = Counter(na), Counter(nb)\n    overlap = sum((ca & cb).values())\n    prec = overlap / (len(nb) + 1e-9)\n    rec = overlap / (len(na) + 1e-9)\n    if prec + rec == 0:\n        f1 = 0.0\n    else:\n        f1 = 2 * prec * rec / (prec + rec)\n    return prec, rec, f1, overlap, len(na), len(nb)\n\ntoken_f1(original_full, candidate)",
